1. input the text to be measured;
    a. store it in a string;
    b. get its lenght;
2. input the measured text:
    a. start timer when a key is pressed in the input field;
    b. store each character in a new string;
    c. chech each entered letter if it matches with its correspondent from the first text.
        i: if it matches: 
                - color it green;
                - count the matched letters;
        ii: if it's different:
                - color it red;
                - count the mistake;
4. stop timer when last letter is written;
3. calculate and display the acuracy

